attributes.title: Probably By far if not Absolutely the worst app
attributes.review: I was very hesitant about downloading this app with everything going on in the world. But i wanted to give Trump the benefit of the doubt. Seconds into dowloading and opening the app my phone glitched. After pressing to not receive notifications my phone went off with at least 20 in a row. This frustrated me soo badly that I soent a week in bed crying. I was hoping this app made me feel proud to be an AFRICAN American in 2020 but it only made me feel like a minority whose voice is silenced my systematic oppression and the white cops fear of my melanin.But that is for another conversation. Basically this app made my life a living hell, which is quite hard to do as is im already part of Gen Z living in the 21st century where people under the age of 21 are seen to have no intelligence and little to none motivation. If I could I would download this app just to figure out the ip address in irder to give it to my great aunts uncle who would send his neighbors dog to the location and poop right in in front of its mailbox. Thanks for hearing my delicate review of the worlds worst app.
